      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Met-ID, a graphical user interface software designed to efficiently identify metabolites from MALDI-MSI data sets... The software is able to identify multiple derivatization sites on the same molecule, facilitating identification of the derivatized compound... While Met-ID can process MS1 and MS2 data independently, a typical MSI workflow involves sequential... Met-ID combines both MS1 and MS2 functionalities.",
