      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Met-ID allows users to customize their own versions... Met-ID also provides tools for calculating and supporting the different masses added by other derivatizing matrices.",
      "asbval:note": "Met-ID is confirmed as the core platform with customization and matrix support. However, the paper does not explicitly mention a 'plugin registry' or 'configuration loader' architecture. The customization is described as user-facing (adding matrices, metabolites, functional groups) but the internal architecture terminology is not used in the passages.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1021-acs-analchem-5c00633",
