      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms Met-ID is available on GitHub and mentions codebase availability, but does not explicitly discuss cloning workflows, CI/CD inspection, or version-control artifact inspection as a task. The paper describes the software's availability and modularity but does not frame Git repository cloning and CI/CD inspection as a reproducibility workflow.",
