      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "To enable Met-ID to be used for any type of MSI experiment, it was developed to be dynamic, i.e., users can add their own metabolites, functional groups and matrices, as well as MS2 spectra to customize their own version of Met-ID.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms extensibility to novel matrices. Accuracy validation is demonstrated through comparisons with chemical standards and tissue samples with known metabolites.",
