      "asbval:note": "Paper describes Met-ID's CI/CD setup (Github Actions compilation) but does not provide instructions or guidance on reproducing the CI/CD pipeline locally. The paper documents that Github Actions exists and compiles code, but does not address the task of setting up a local shell environment to mirror CI/CD execution.",
